        "mode": "html",
        "content": "<div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a5f 0%, #2d4a6f 50%, #3d5a7f 100%); padding: 40px 24px; color: white; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif;\">\n  <h1 style=\"font-size: 28px; font-weight: 300; margin: 0 0 12px 0; letter-spacing: -0.5px;\">Swiss Open Government Data</h1>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px; opacity: 0.9; max-width: 680px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 20px 0;\">Explore datasets from the LINDAS Linked Data Service. Browse cubes from Swiss federal offices and create visualizations.</p>\n</div>"
